{"tid":2120140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司法機構無懼疫情照開庭 有被告曾與確診大狀客戶接觸未能應訊","createTime":"2020-07-22T13:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T13:29:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a5b568ce8da16441293ef70d58b114eb1fcd43","tid":2120140,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/37RURNGZUQTRRAI336Z7CY2CK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2F37RURNGZUQTRRAI336Z7CY2CK4%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=048d4bdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2F37RURNGZUQTRRAI336Z7CY2CK4%2F&h=8a077969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/37RURNGZUQTRRAI336Z7CY2CK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續失控，衛生署剛公佈昨日有113宗確診個案，破單日新高。不過，司法機構無懼疫情，經歷過去兩日有限度停擺後，今日重開法庭。惟高等法院今日多宗涉及販毒的案件，由於還柙中被告曾與日前確診的大狀李家齊所代表的被告有接觸，需接受隔離並等候病毒測試結果，故無法開庭。另有作供證人起初應要求脫下口罩作供，但中途表示欲戴回，坦言「見個庭愈嚟愈多人，保護返屋企人」，惟遭裁判官拒絕。"},{"pid":"ba403cb47686a957b1e90966946f1e954cdc37b8","tid":2120140,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"ce3e471a01afd9beeb95bdcf57d67ea64ad7ddbc","tid":2120140,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"今日唔係話開始室內強制戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}